            <p class="animate">
            This is an ever changing blog.
            This site will never try to make money off you. This includes selling any information to third party advertisers. 
            Writing and researching these topics will be time consuming, exhausting, error prone, hit-my-head-against-a-wall-difficult, but I hope inspires you in a small way, even it means 
            </p>
        </article>
